INCEPTION

	Makefile
		-sets up entire application
		-builds Docker images using docker-compose.yml
	srcs folder
		-all files



	Use docker compose
	Docker Compose
		-define && manage multi-container Docker applications
		-uses YAML file (docker-compose.yml)
			-configures
				i. services	(Nginx = server && Wordpress = site ???)
				ii. networks (???)
				iii. volumes (f.ex. MariaDB)
		-starts with single command
			docker-compose up



